node.html: A FreeCodeCamp Project. This site will display random quotes using the Forismatic API. You can see the code and learn to work with API and front end. If you want, you can tweet the quotes. It will take you to a new page where you won't need to edit the post, because it brings only quotes below 140 characters.

Pomofocus is a customizable pomodoro timer that works on desktop & mobile browser. The aim of this app is to help you focus on any task you are working on, such as study, writing, or coding. This app is inspired by Pomodoro Technique which is a time management method developed by Francesco Cirillo.
